Author: luplum
Text: This is me anytime someone says they're dieting or they skipped a meal. Suddenly Miss Health over here.

Author: throwaway71871127198
Text: I’m always such a fucking hypocrite and it gets worse the more I restrict. If I’m eating semi-normally I’ll barely notice how other people are eating but as soon as I’m restricting more I’m all “omg have you eaten yet today? Can I make you something? It’s so important to eat three meals a day! Oh dw I already ate :) you should eat too!!” while sitting there with no food in front of me
